_sText:
The card is in order to save (defuse) hostage with the aid of the input code or a special key.

At a location on the map is a room containing a hidden bomb hostage.

This map is implemented with a combination lock code "1 8 2 7 3 5"

Go into a room can only Vip player. If you have no time to defuse a hostage, an explosion and all dissent will die.
